<br>
How great would that be?  Only problem I see with items like this is that AC is so much more important for melees.  Whereas a wizard is happy to give up that AC6 bracer for an AC0 Gallenite's Jade Bracelet that increases DDs +20%, a melee might lose considerably more trading that AC20 bracer for an AC2 summoned bracelet.  And any armour items that had both good AC and a focus would probably be exhorbitantly priced.<br>
<br>
